The paper is about optimal and learning control for autonomous robots, which is a topic that falls under the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The paper also discusses reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of Machine Learning (cs.LG). The course assumes basic knowledge of Control Theory (cs.SY) and Stochastic Calculus, which are also mentioned in the abstract. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of computer vision (cs.CV) for autonomous robots, which is another possible sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the use of algorithms for closed loop control problems, which is a topic that falls under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI).
